# Memory Server API Tests
# Use with VSCode REST Client extension
# Install: ext install humao.rest-client

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8001
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. System Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. API Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs
Accept: text/html

### 4. List Workspaces
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/workspaces
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 5. Document Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/stats
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 6. Web Search (without API key - will show error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/web
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "query": "Python machine learning",
    "max_results": 3
}

### 7. Search Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/config
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8. Health Detailed
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/detailed
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9. Health Metrics  
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/metrics
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 10. Document Activity Log
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/activity
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "action": "test",
    "details": "API test from VSCode"
}

### 11. Content Summarization
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/summarize/content
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "content": "Artificial Intelligence is transforming the world. Machine learning algorithms are becoming more sophisticated each day. Deep learning has enabled breakthroughs in computer vision and natural language processing.",
    "summary_type": "brief"
}

### 12. Available Summary Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/summarize/types
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 13. Create Workspace Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/workspace/test
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Test Document",
    "content": "This is a test document for the Memory Server. It contains information about artificial intelligence and machine learning.",
    "metadata": {
        "source": "vscode-test",
        "category": "testing",
        "tags": ["ai", "ml", "test"]
    }
}

### 14. Search in Documents  
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/search?query=artificial%20intelligence&workspace=test
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 15. Documentation Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/documentation
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "query": "how to use memory server API",
    "domain": "localhost"
}

### 16. Code Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/code
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "query": "async def initialize",
    "language": "python",
    "file_types": [".py"]
}

### 17. Health Status Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/status
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 18. Health Ready Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 19. Health Live Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 20. OpenAPI Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
Accept: {{contentType}}

###